'''格蘭·森美爾·麥肯'''（{{lang-en|'''Grant Samuel McCann'''}}，{{bd|1980年|4月14日|catidx=McCann, Grant}}）在[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[首府|首府]][[贝尔法斯特|贝尔法斯特]]出生，是一名退役職業足球員，司職[[中場|中場]]，曾是彼德堡的[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，他亦是前[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭]]國腳。麥肯曾於效力[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]、[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]及[[皮特堡联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]時，在三個不同的球場分別協助球隊透過附加賽取得升班資格。現時執教[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[彼德堡聯足球會|彼德堡]]。

==生平==
===球會===
====早年====
麥肯幼年時曾參加[[利斯本|利斯本]]青年隊（Lisburn Youth team），與[[大衞·希利|大衞·希利]]、[[艾朗·曉士|艾朗·曉士]]、[[萨米·克林甘|萨米·克林甘]]、[[乔尼·埃文斯|乔尼·埃文斯]]等為先後隊友<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.lisburnyouth.co.uk/aboutus/aboutus.html |title=About Us – Lisburn Youth Football Club Online |publisher=''Lisburnyouth.co.uk'' |date= |accessdate=2011-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101130233700/http://www.lisburnyouth.co.uk/aboutus/aboutus.html |archivedate=2010-11-30 }}</ref>。其後由家鄉遠赴[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[倫敦|倫敦]]投效[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，於足球學院畢業後<ref name=Alumni>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.whufc.com/page/AcademyAlumni |title=West Ham United Academy Graduates |publisher=''Whufc.com'' |date= |accessdate=2011-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117231115/http://www.whufc.com/page/AcademyAlumni |archivedate=2011-11-17 }}</ref>，開始展開職業足球事業，並在2001年5月19日取得一隊首次上陣機會，作客1-2負於[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/1338640.stm |title=Karembeu winner sinks Hammers |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2001-05-19 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307224042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/1338640.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

未能晉身一隊的常規陣容，麥肯曾獲外借到多支低級別球隊汲取上陣經驗，先後短暫加盟[[利文斯顿足球俱乐部|利雲斯頓]]和[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]，直到2000年再被借用到身處第四級丙組聯賽的[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2193767,00.html |title=McCANN LOANED TO CHELTENHAM |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2000-10-20 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309150540/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2193767,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年後麥肯再次以借用身份返回車頓咸<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2246813,00.html |title=McCann makes Whaddon Road return |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2002-10-04 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085311/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2246813,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後獲延長借用至翌年1月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2251549,00.html |title=Hammers agree McCann extension |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2002-11-29 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085324/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2251549,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於12月17日被韋斯咸提前召回以應付繁忙的聖誕新年賽期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2252058,00.html |title=McCann makes Hammers return |publisher=S''ky Sports'' |date=2002-12-17 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085331/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2252058,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====車頓咸====
2003年1月28日[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]以破球會記錄的5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]正式羅致麥肯，簽約兩年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2256185,00.html |title=Gould makes first signing |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-01-28 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308014512/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2256185,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麥肯於效力這支[[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]]球隊四年期間在聯賽上陣158場及射入31球。2006年1月12日麥肯需要上手術床治理較早前受傷的[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]，預計需要缺陣6星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11744_2362876,00.html |title=McCann goes under the knife |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-01-10 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309152349/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11744_2362876,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麥肯康復後協助球隊取得聯賽第5位可以參加升班附加賽，準決賽兩回合累計2-1淘汰[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韋甘比]]，5月28日在[[千禧球場|千禧球場]]決賽與[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|甘士比]]，險勝1-0取得最後一個升班[[英甲|英甲]]席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/5010270.stm |title=Grimsby 0-1 Cheltenham |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-05-28 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214141506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/5010270.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。升班後麥肯保持勇態，上半季射入7球而成為球隊的首席射手，但車頓咸卻位處降班區域正在掙扎求存，而將於季後約滿的麥肯亦意向不明<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11744_2395528,00.html |title=Robins wait for McCann |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-11-14 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041407/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11744_2395528,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====班士利====
在借用球員限期最後一天的2006年11月23日，麥肯先以借用身份效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]，待[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開後才正式加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11713_2396570,00.html |title=Busy Tykes secure third deal |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-11-23 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090808/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11713_2396570,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月25日首次披甲主場迎戰[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，於完場前的92分鐘射入奠勝球，為新任領隊[[西蒙·戴维|西蒙·戴维]]（Simon Davey）首仗執教帶來勝利<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6160986.stm |title=Barnsley 1-0 Ipswich |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-11-25 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812015024/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6160986.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。班士利與車頓咸達成協議，於2007年1月3日以10萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]收購麥肯，簽約至2009年夏季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.irishfa.com/news/item/2679/mccann-signs-for-barnsley |title=Mccann Signs For Barnsley |publisher=''Irishfa.com'' |date=2007-01-03 |accessdate=2011-05-30 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130010629/https://www.irishfa.com/news/item/2679/mccann-signs-for-barnsley |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦是當時車頓咸賣出球員收取最高的轉會費記錄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/6684035.stm |title=Tykes sign Cheltenham's Odejayi |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-05-31 |accessdate=2011-05-30 |archive-date=2008-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080315150505/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/6684035.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]季初麥肯一度被貶為板凳球員，因而向領隊西蒙·戴维表明需要更多上陣時間以爭取入選[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|國家隊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2721532,00.html |title=McCann wants Barnsley role |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-09-11 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085400/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_2721532,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====斯肯索普====
2008年1月8日班士利表示接獲另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]求購麥肯，但以出價太低而拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/7176315.stm |title=Trio transfer-listed by Barnsley |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-08 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2008-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118225303/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/7176315.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1月15日麥肯最終可以轉投斯肯索普，轉會費金額沒有透露，簽約兩年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/7190407.stm |title=McCann completes Scunthorpe move |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-15 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2008-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118161042/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/7190407.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而麥肯為班士利射入最後的一球正正是在[[元旦|元旦]]對斯肯索普，雙方2-2平手完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7163886.stm |title=Scunthorpe 2-2 Barnsley |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-01-01 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811055201/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7163886.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但麥肯的加盟亦不能阻止球隊於[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|球季]]結束後降班返回[[英甲|英甲]]。[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]麥肯為斯肯索普在各項賽事合共上陣多達58場，取得12個入球。於[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]勇闖決賽，惟經[[加時賽|加時賽]]以2-3不敵[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]屈居亞軍<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7975143.stm |title=Luton 3-2 Scunthorpe (aet) |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-04-05 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2009-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408040739/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7975143.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。聯賽煞科日於完場前1-1追平[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|燦美爾]]，力壓對手取得最後一個附加賽參賽席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8014943.stm |title=Scunthorpe 1-1 Tranmere |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-02 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815032823/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8014943.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。附加賽準決賽兩回合累計1-1賽和[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米爾頓凱恩斯]]，憑[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]7-6險勝過關；2009年5月24日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]對陣[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]，以3-2獲勝取得最後一張[[英冠|英冠]]的入場劵<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |title=Millwall 2-3 Scunthorpe |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-05-24 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2009-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527093943/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[斯肯索普2009年至2010年球季|2009/10年球季]]麥肯保持佳態，到10月中已射入6球，是球隊的平頭領先射手之一，但於季後約滿的麥肯表示斯肯索普沒有與他商討續約問題<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8318380.stm |title=No new Iron deal yet for McCann |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-10-21 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814173150/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8318380.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====彼德堡====
2010年5月24日剛降班[[英甲|英甲]]的[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]宣佈擊退多支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊，取得麥肯首肯免費加盟，簽訂三年合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8700531.stm |title=Peterborough sign Grant McCann on three-year deal |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-24 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813014813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8700531.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Posh pull off major Transfer coup |url=http://www.theposh.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10427~2057997,00.html |publisher=[[皮特堡联足球俱乐部|''theposh.com'']] |date=24 May 2010 |accessdate=24 May 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526021126/http://www.theposh.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10427~2057997,00.html |archivedate=2010年5月26日 }}</ref>。8月1日麥肯接替[[乔治·博伊德|乔治·博伊德]]擔任球隊的[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8877758.stm |title=Grant McCann confirmed as Peterborough United captain |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815051543/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8877758.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月7日他於聯賽揭幕戰主場對[[布里斯托尔流浪者足球俱乐部|布里斯托流浪]]初次登場並取得入球，鎖定3-0勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8842035.stm |title=Peterborough 3-0 Bristol Rovers |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-07 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814091845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8842035.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；9月28日主場2-3負於[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]，麥肯遭[[球證|球證]]直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場，於鳴笛完場後雙方球員圍攏發生衝突<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9031868.stm |title=Peterborough 2-3 Notts County |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-28 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309191818/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9031868.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後被罰停賽3場，彼德堡於他缺陣期間輸掉兩場賽事，有統計顯示球隊有他在陣的9戰僅兩負，於他缺陣的6場輸了4場，突顯他在隊中的重要性<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9095192.stm |title=Grant McCann makes light of Peterborough United role |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-15 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811013211/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9095192.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年1月15日作客[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]是[[达伦·弗格森|达伦·弗格森]]回巢任教的首仗，麥肯又因領得第二面[[黃牌|黃牌]]被趕離場，季內第二次見[[紅牌|紅]]，最終1-3落敗而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9359261.stm |title=Brighton 3-1 Peterborough |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-15 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209132216/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9359261.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月7日煞科日主場5-0擊敗[[达根汉姆和雷德布里奇足球俱乐部|杜根咸]]麥肯亦有一球進帳<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13247270.stm |title=Peterborough 5-0 Dag & Red |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-07 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2011-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510144034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13247270.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，球隊以第四位的成績結束[[彼德堡2010年至2011年球季|球季]]參加附加賽，準決賽兩回合累計4-3淘汰[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米爾頓凱恩斯]]，麥肯兩回合各入一球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13325757.stm |title=MK Dons 3-2 Peterborough |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-15 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109005959/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13325757.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13370673.stm |title=Peterborough 2-0 MK Dons (agg 4-3) |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-19 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2011-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522132414/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13370673.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；5月27日決賽在[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]迎擊[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]，麥肯再入一球為球隊鎖定3-0勝局，取得升班[[英冠|英冠]]資格<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13489373.stm |title=Huddersfield 0-3 Peterborough |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-29 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109005713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13489373.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加盟首季麥肯在各項賽事合共上陣49場及射入13球，更以21個助攻成為英甲的助攻王。

2011/12年球季季中有傳爭取升班的[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]有意羅致麥肯，尚餘18個月合約的麥肯隨即表示希望留隊直至退役<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15778952.stm |title=Grant McCann keen to stay with Peterborough United |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-11-17 |accessdate=2011-11-18 |archive-date=2011-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111218100335/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15778952.stm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年12月10日作客1-1賽和[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]，麥肯下半場受傷離場，賽後證實膝蓋內側副韧带撕裂，需要缺陣10星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16137411.stm |title=Peterborough United's Grant McCann hit by knee injury |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-12-12 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2012-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111165957/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16137411.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
麥肯曾代表[[北愛爾蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭U21]]上陣11場及射入3球。他於2001年10月7日首次代表[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|成年國家隊]]上陣，作客以1-0擊敗[[馬爾他國家足球隊|馬爾他]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2002/1576746.stm |title=Healy makes Malta pay penalty |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2001-10-07 |accessdate=2011- |archive-date=2003-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030306110434/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2002/1576746.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2002年3月27日麥肯首次以正選身份上陣作客對[[列支敦士登国家足球队|列支敦士登]]，因撞傷而需用擔架抬離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2002/1895316.stm |title=NI held by lowly Liechtenstein |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2002-03-27 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121222852/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2002/1895316.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]內側韌帶破損而需休養5星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2233815,00.html |title=McCann debut ends in disaster |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2002-03-28 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085301/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11685_2233815,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年3月24日作客4-1擊敗[[列支敦士登国家足球队|列支敦士登]]，麥肯頂入已隊最後一球取得首個國際賽入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6473569.stm |title=Liechtenstein 1-4 N Ireland |publisher=''[[BBC體育|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-03-24 |accessdate=2011-10-19 |archive-date=2009-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331133828/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6473569.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

